据拟合得比较可以。进一步，通过方程(20)和图4可以计算得到，最优的二次爆破单耗成本为1.3908元/千克。</p><table-wrap id="table5" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table5">Table 5</xref></label><caption><title> Calculation results of the unit cost of secondary blasting by the quadratic polynomial curve mode</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >序号</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >二次爆破单耗成本(元/千克)</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >二次多项式计算结果</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >APE (%)</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.2222</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.1820</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−1.8106</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.7188</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.9961</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >16.1386</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.0155</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.8351</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−8.9497</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.7557</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.6990</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−3.2331</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.5789</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.5876</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.5507</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >6</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.3971</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.5012</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >7.4523</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >7</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.4483</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.4395</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >−0.6027</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >8</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.5068</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.4028</